Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.40,0:00:23.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}綁架事件總是會要求贖金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.20,0:00:24.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}一般情況下都以錢為目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.00,0:00:26.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}今天的事件總覺得怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.10,0:00:28.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}唯一看清真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.50,0:00:30.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}看上去是小孩  頭腦卻是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.20,0:00:32.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}他的名字是名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.20,0:02:13.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}兩點半啊 真是令人昏昏欲睡的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.70,0:02:23.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.10,0:02:25.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}快報警
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.10,0:02:27.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}救護車 快叫救護車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.00,0:02:35.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}已經沒必要叫救護車了 是當場死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.70,0:02:37.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}以那麼快的速度駕駛不出事才怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.50,0:02:39.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}打方向盤已經來不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.50,0:02:49.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎麼會有這麼多錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.30,0:02:52.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}真厲害 這是什麼 信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.20,0:02:54.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.20,0:02:59.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這是3千萬元 沒有通知警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.20,0:03:02.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}快把我父親送回來 堂本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.50,0:03:04.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這麼說來這些錢是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.10,0:03:08.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}為換回人質而準備的贖金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.70,0:03:16.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}疑似綁架事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.50,0:03:30.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}死者是平野猛 因恐嚇罪被逮捕過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.80,0:03:33.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}已經比對過犯人的照片了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.50,0:03:37.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}應該是在把贖金拿回去的路上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.20,0:03:41.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}如果他是獨自作案的話就糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.30,0:03:45.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}知道人質關押地點的人就沒有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.50,0:03:47.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不但如此 時間還很緊迫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.10,0:03:51.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我父親有腎病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.20,0:03:53.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}每隔6小時就要服藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.20,0:03:55.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}否則會有生命危險 藥已經裝在信封裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.30,0:03:56.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}請無論如何要把藥交給我父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.60,0:04:03.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就是說這個藥還沒有交到人質的手中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.20,0:04:04.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不快點交過去就會有生命危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.00,0:04:07.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}那麼人質到底被監禁在哪裡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.20,0:04:12.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}綁架事件如果不知道被綁架的人是誰就沒轍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.30,0:04:15.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}雖然知道姓堂本 但是是哪裡的堂本呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.40,0:04:17.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}他應該經常會去醫院吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.80,0:04:18.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}為了拿藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.50,0:04:30.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我們是米花電器 您買的電視機已經到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.90,0:04:34.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那個 你們是不是搞錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.30,0:04:37.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不會搞錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.50,0:04:40.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}總之請你先看看定購單確認一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.10,0:04:44.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那個 我們沒有買電視機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.50,0:04:50.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.90,0:04:52.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.00,0:04:54.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.80,0:04:59.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}好久不見 大學的學長 是我呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.20,0:05:00.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我是他的兒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.00,0:05:02.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}初次見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.50,0:05:05.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}為什麼你也來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.50,0:05:07.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}帶著小孩子不容易被懷疑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.90,0:05:11.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我們是來調查綁架事件的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.90,0:05:12.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.90,0:05:15.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}父親他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.10,0:05:21.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}定期到市中心的醫院治療腎衰竭的堂本先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.00,0:05:27.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就是在米花中心醫院做檢查的堂本正三郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.50,0:05:28.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我們已經知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.00,0:05:30.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}但是你們為什麼會知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.50,0:05:32.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}他們說通知了警察爸爸的性命就不保了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.40,0:05:36.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}情況發生了改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.40,0:05:38.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}為什麼這些錢會到你們警察手裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.60,0:05:41.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}我明明已經把錢放到他們指定的地方了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.30,0:05:44.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}那個犯人騎摩托車出事故死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.00,0:05:45.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.70,0:05:47.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k70}犯人他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.00,0:05:49.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}請不要放棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.10,0:05:52.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}我們正在調查犯人的人際關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.40,0:05:56.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}不知道是否能追查到關押你父親的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.10,0:05:59.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這個竟然沒能交到爸爸的手中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.20,0:06:04.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}每隔6小時 你父親最後接受注射是什麼時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.50,0:06:05.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}今天早上9點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.10,0:06:10.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}那麼接下去是下午3點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.80,0:06:13.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不是已經過了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.70,0:06:16.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.50,0:06:21.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}並不是馬上就會出狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.20,0:06:24.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是超過8個小時的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.60,0:06:26.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就是說8小時是極限了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.00,0:06:30.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}時限就是5點 只剩下1個半小時了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.00,0:06:36.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你父親是什麼時候 怎麼被綁架的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.10,0:06:38.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}還有犯人和你們是怎麼接觸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.50,0:06:40.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}請詳細告訴我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.60,0:06:42.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}我們家是4個人一起住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.60,0:06:46.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}經營金屬加工的父親堂本正三郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.60,0:06:50.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}唯一的女兒我 我的丈夫秋成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.70,0:06:53.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}以及管家須籐昌代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.80,0:06:56.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}今天是公司開業紀念日 大家都休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.00,0:06:59.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以早上起來後我們就都在家裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.70,0:07:02.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}我也在爸爸的公司工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.40,0:07:07.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}女兒和女婿將來就是繼承者了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.70,0:07:17.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}早上9點幫爸爸注射之後我就到朋友家裡去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.10,0:07:25.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}今天外出是早就約好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.10,0:07:28.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}然後爸爸就去散步了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.30,0:07:30.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}這是他休息日的習慣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.70,0:07:33.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}10點左右我來到我的書房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.90,0:07:36.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}有好多要整理的文件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.60,0:07:42.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}11點左右我在打掃浴室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.40,0:07:43.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}然後電話響了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.60,0:07:45.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}是個年輕男子的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.60,0:07:47.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}把電話交給家裡的其他人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.20,0:07:50.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我是堂本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.20,0:07:53.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}什麼 綁架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.80,0:07:59.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}也就是說 堂本正三郎是在外出散步的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.30,0:08:02.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}也就是上午9點半到11點之間被綁架的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.30,0:08:10.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}散步有固定的路線嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.20,0:08:12.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}是的 基本一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.10,0:08:13.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}在哪些地方呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.70,0:08:17.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}這個給你 也許能知道監禁地的線索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.10,0:08:20.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我去找找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.90,0:08:26.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}於是我急忙把妻子叫了回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.30,0:08:32.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}犯人要求的3千萬日元我來想辦法湊齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.40,0:08:33.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不要緊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.00,0:08:36.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}只要付了錢爸爸就會平安地回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.10,0:08:38.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}交給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.70,0:08:41.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}拜託了 秋成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.80,0:08:54.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這樣就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.10,0:08:57.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}秋成 謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.90,0:09:06.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}喂 把贖金…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.50,0:09:23.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}他說確認了錢後就把人質送回來 讓我們在家裡等著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.60,0:09:25.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我們那麼相信他的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.70,0:09:29.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}以防萬一把藥也裝在信封裡了 卻…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.90,0:09:33.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}4點了 還有1小時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.50,0:09:36.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不要哭 爸爸一定會平安地回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.90,0:09:40.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是的 總會希望他平安吧 不管平時怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.40,0:09:52.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}毛利叔叔叫我來問一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.80,0:09:56.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}剛才的那句"不管平時怎樣"是什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.70,0:10:03.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那個 老爺以前曾經給秋成先生留下痛苦的回憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.60,0:10:05.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}痛苦的回憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.20,0:10:11.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}怎麼回事 你沒發現那是個圈套嗎 你真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.70,0:10:15.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我也是為了公司才拚命地…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.90,0:10:19.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你終究沒有成為我接班人的才能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.40,0:10:21.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}光看你的臉就沒食慾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.60,0:10:23.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.80,0:10:26.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}為什麼老爺會說出那種話呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.80,0:10:29.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}這對秋成先生也太嚴厲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.80,0:10:32.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是這種時候夫人總會幫秋成先生吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.90,0:10:33.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這個嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.00,0:10:37.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}剛結婚的時候真是關係非常好的一對夫妻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.00,0:10:40.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但最近連光子小姐也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.20,0:10:43.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你不覺得丟臉嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.90,0:10:47.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}被那樣說 虧你還是個男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.20,0:10:52.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}光子 為什麼連你也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.60,0:10:54.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}果然還是受了父親的影響呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.10,0:10:57.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}但被綁架了就不同了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.70,0:11:02.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}秋成先生也很擔心並且在祈禱老爺平安無事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.80,0:11:06.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以才那麼拚命地去籌錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.10,0:11:14.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}大概是這樣吧 和綁架案沒什麼關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.80,0:11:19.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.70,0:11:21.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}根據平野猛的朋友說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.80,0:11:25.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}一周前他好像突然變得威風起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.40,0:11:29.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就是說他被人用錢僱用了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.30,0:11:35.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}恐怕是這樣 但僱用他的人是誰還不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.10,0:11:37.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}幕後真兇還不清楚嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.60,0:11:39.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}繼續追查他的人際關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.10,0:11:43.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}如果知道那個人是誰就能找到監禁地的線索了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.20,0:11:46.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}幕後指使者另有其人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.20,0:11:48.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}如果是這樣就很奇怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.40,0:11:49.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}總覺得有點奇怪 警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.70,0:11:50.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.00,0:11:53.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}幕後指使者如果一直等不到取贖金的人回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.70,0:11:55.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}通常都應該會打個電話來催
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.00,0:12:00.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}但他為什麼沒來電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.20,0:12:03.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}難道他準備就這樣算了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.30,0:12:04.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}原來如此 是有點奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.10,0:12:06.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}正是如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.60,0:12:11.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}既然是要錢那指使的人為什麼不來追討呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.00,0:12:16.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.20,0:12:17.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}光子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.10,0:12:20.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k90}莫非這起綁架的真正目的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.90,0:12:28.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}原來是這樣 這麼一想的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.50,0:12:31.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎麼又來了 小傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.00,0:12:36.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}秋成先生早上一直呆在自己的書房裡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.70,0:12:38.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是啊 有工作要做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.10,0:12:40.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}那個時候他對你說了些什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.90,0:12:43.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}說了什麼 這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.90,0:12:47.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}昌代管家 我要專心工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.30,0:12:48.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就不要送茶過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.80,0:12:51.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}果然是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.80,0:12:53.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.00,0:13:11.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}機械潤滑油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.70,0:13:24.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我明白了 這起綁架事件的真兇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.70,0:13:27.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是如果逼問他的話他一定會裝糊塗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.60,0:13:29.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}然後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.00,0:13:32.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}目的不是錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.50,0:13:35.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}那才是犯人真正的目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.90,0:13:36.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}已經4點半了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.60,0:13:37.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k70}還有半小時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.20,0:13:40.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}到底在哪裡 監禁人質的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.80,0:13:50.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}小鬼頭 你看地圖有什麼用啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.70,0:13:54.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我在想那輛摩托打算到哪兒去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.20,0:13:57.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那還用說 當然是監禁人質的地方啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.70,0:14:01.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以 從拿到贖金的米花公園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.60,0:14:04.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}到案發現場的這條線的前邊就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.70,0:14:08.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}或許如此吧 不過 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.40,0:14:13.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}你能判斷出這條延長線是10米還是100米嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.00,0:14:16.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這裡的名字和這家人的名字…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.60,0:14:19.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}堂本金屬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.20,0:14:22.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}那是我家的工廠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.60,0:14:26.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}但是在半年前 東米花的新廠房建成後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.60,0:14:28.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那裡就關閉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.30,0:14:30.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}也就是說 是一處廢棄工廠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.20,0:14:34.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}那麼 那裡也就不會有人去了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.20,0:14:36.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}警官 作為監禁地點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.90,0:14:38.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}十分有可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.70,0:14:40.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}柯南 把地圖給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.20,0:14:41.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.50,0:14:43.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}那 爸爸他就在那個工廠裡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.00,0:14:45.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}有這個可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.40,0:14:48.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}只有15分鐘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.40,0:14:53.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}夫人 不到最後 就不能放棄希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.80,0:14:55.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}說得好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.90,0:14:58.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}還剩15分鐘 一定要趕上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.10,0:15:10.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}給我停住 時間給我停住啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.80,0:15:12.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.40,0:15:25.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}給我 讓我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.80,0:15:30.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.20,0:15:32.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}堂本先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.80,0:15:40.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.80,0:15:41.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.10,0:15:53.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}爸爸 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.00,0:15:56.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}還有呼吸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.70,0:16:00.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}我是高木 要救護車 地點是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.40,0:16:11.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}堂本先生 振作一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.20,0:16:23.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}夫人要隨車一起去醫院了 您也請
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.40,0:16:24.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.50,0:16:29.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}您請等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.90,0:16:31.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.60,0:16:34.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}變成沉睡的小五郎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.60,0:16:36.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.90,0:16:41.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我相信堂本先生能平安脫險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.00,0:16:46.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}秋成先生 你似乎在盼望著相反的結果啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.70,0:16:52.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}盼望著 相反的結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.10,0:16:52.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這話什麼意思呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.60,0:16:57.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}我是在搞清楚了這宗綁架案的目的並非贖金時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.10,0:16:58.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}才注意到這一點的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.90,0:17:02.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}據柯南從管家昌代那裡打聽到的情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.30,0:17:06.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你和光子小姐是相愛而結婚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.00,0:17:09.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是 入贅進入堂本家後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.60,0:17:11.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}卻被堂本先生責備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.30,0:17:16.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}沒有霸氣 不是做繼承人的料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.30,0:17:19.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}開始了難熬的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.00,0:17:23.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}當然你就恨上了堂本先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.80,0:17:26.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}想要把他從這個世上給除掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.20,0:17:29.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.60,0:17:32.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}可是 你卻沒這個膽量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.50,0:17:35.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}所以就計劃了這次的事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.70,0:17:37.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.10,0:17:40.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}怎麼會 怎麼回事 我什麼都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.30,0:17:44.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不 犯人就是這個秋成先生 目暮警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.20,0:17:47.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不 這怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.20,0:17:50.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}堂本先生是在散步的時候被綁架的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.50,0:17:52.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}當時秋成先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.50,0:17:54.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}我當時在書房辦公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.90,0:17:57.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}真是這樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.40,0:17:59.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}進入了書房的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.70,0:18:03.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}昌代管家 我要專心工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.40,0:18:04.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就不要送茶過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.40,0:18:10.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就這樣 支開了昌代管家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.50,0:18:13.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你穿上了準備好的鞋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.50,0:18:23.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}追上了正在散步的堂本先生 讓他上了車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.30,0:18:27.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你究竟想說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.50,0:18:31.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}帶我到這種地方來 你這個男人真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.20,0:18:34.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}有什麼想說的就快點…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.40,0:18:39.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不好 糟了 得快點回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.70,0:18:41.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我沒帶藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.10,0:19:00.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}秋成先生 您的電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.20,0:19:08.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}什麼 綁架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.80,0:19:12.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}就這樣 你開始扮演起滿臉無辜的被害者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.80,0:19:16.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}當然 證據是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.70,0:19:18.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}書房的窗台上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.80,0:19:21.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}應該留有和這間工廠的地板上染著的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.20,0:19:24.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}有著相同顏色的機械潤滑油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.50,0:19:27.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這就是你從窗子進出過的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.80,0:19:30.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}慌忙之中用來將它擦去的餐巾紙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.40,0:19:32.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}肯定就扔在那房間的某個角落裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.60,0:19:34.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}還有更有力的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.80,0:19:36.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}就是你留在地面上的進出時的腳印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.80,0:19:42.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}驅車從堂本家到這裡來回要花1個小時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.50,0:19:44.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以你是有可能作案的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.20,0:19:48.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}就在你獨自呆在書房裡的10點到11點之間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.90,0:19:53.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}的確有可能 但為什麼要自己動手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.90,0:19:57.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}讓拿了贖金的那個姓平野的男人去做不就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.70,0:20:03.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那個男的恐怕並不知道他是在幫人綁架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.60,0:20:05.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不知道他是在幫人綁架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.40,0:20:08.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}當時他委託了平野的只有兩點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.50,0:20:09.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}給我打個電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.50,0:20:11.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}上午11點和下午2點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.00,0:20:15.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}另外一件事是從米花公園替我把一個手提箱拿來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.20,0:20:17.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}裡邊裝的什麼 我是什麼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.40,0:20:19.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}這些事情你最好不要知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.20,0:20:23.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}如果你說出了計劃 就會被他抓住把柄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.10,0:20:27.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}然後 你就在夫人出門去了的今天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.20,0:20:28.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}實施了計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.90,0:20:31.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}什麼 綁架了爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.70,0:20:34.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}贖金 米花公園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.90,0:20:37.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}也就是說 電話是一出獨角戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.30,0:20:51.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}沒錯 要是那個平野沒發生交通事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.70,0:20:53.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不但能在之後把錢收回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.90,0:20:57.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}而且這個計劃也就順利地完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.10,0:21:00.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}警察和偵探也不會出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.60,0:21:04.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}只要在一旁裝成擔心堂本先生的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.30,0:21:06.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}等在那裡就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.90,0:21:09.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你說的沒錯 但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.00,0:21:12.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}動機卻並非是你說的那樣 毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.10,0:21:16.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}的確 我恨那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.90,0:21:18.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}想著他要是死了就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.50,0:21:20.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}但並不是僅此而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.70,0:21:24.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}我裝出拚命籌錢的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.40,0:21:25.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}是做給光子看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.70,0:21:29.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}只要她看到我這麼拚命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.50,0:21:32.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就能重新找回她對我的愛情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.90,0:23:05.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我是光子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.40,0:23:08.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}太好了 爸爸他終於脫險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.70,0:23:11.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}等他醒過來的時候我會對他說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.10,0:23:14.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}你曾那樣拚命地奔走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.30,0:23:16.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那樣地為他擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.30,0:23:20.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}爸爸他也就不會再故意氣你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.80,0:23:22.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}故意的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.40,0:23:27.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}爸爸他為了讓你成為稱職的繼承人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.20,0:23:29.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}故意演了一場戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.70,0:23:33.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}因為爸爸其實很喜歡秋成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.30,0:23:35.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}只要能改掉你那過於死板的性格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.30,0:23:40.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我最近也模仿著爸爸 演了一場戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.20,0:23:42.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}其實我很不情願的 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.90,0:23:46.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}喂 喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.40,0:23:48.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}秋成 喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.50,0:24:02.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}罪犯的真正目的究竟是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.70,0:24:05.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}還有600名乘客的性命將會怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.20,0:24:07.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}現在毫無退路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.50,0:24:09.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}就快要到界限的時間懸念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.00,0:24:12.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}劇場版新作 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.20,0:24:13.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}水平線上的陰謀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.20,0:24:16.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那部大紅大紫的電影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.40,0:24:17.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}初次於電視上登場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.60,0:24:20.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}第2次發生於1千米上空的懸念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.70,0:24:21.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}春假的電影特輯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.00,0:24:23.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}名偵探柯南 銀翼的魔術師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.10,0:24:26.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}3月28日（週一）晚7：00播出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:27.30,0:24:29.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我喜歡你 新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:45.40,0:24:47.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}NEXT CONAN'S HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:47.40,0:24:48.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}誰 誰在說話啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:48.20,0:24:49.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k80}石頭勾玉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.10,0:24:50.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}下周是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.80,0:24:51.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k70}魔術的休止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.10,0:24:52.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.60,0:24:53.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k50}禁慾的魔術師
